  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to develop a questionnaire to measure patient satisfaction with
      their breast surgery. This questionnaire will help surgeons better understand how patients
      feel about their surgical results. We hope that such a questionnaire will improve the
      understanding of breast surgery results and patient care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
